&lt;li&gt;[curl 官方文档：Content-Disposition](&lt;a href="https://curl.se/docs/features.html#Content-Disposition)"&gt;https://curl.se/docs/features.html#Content-Disposition)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
